Life’s a journey, fatherhood is my guide. 👨‍👦
Prayers to those affected in Maui, & glad this vacation was one ill never forget 🙏

Never thought I’d be able to afford the things I can now growing up the way I did. 🚗 

Im glad I took the road less traveled at a young age, and had all the lessons I did then that prepared me for now.

Flipped phones/electronics at 16 years old on Craigslist

Then started flipping cars a few years later from tow yards 

Fast forward to now, flipping houses in my 20’s

Then buying and keeping rentals, scaling our company, building other companies.

Next stop, flipping commercial buildings and businesses 🙏

No handouts, no favors, no college degree, just all hard work 💪

Here’s the situation

Instead of making a 15k assignment on this duplex wholesaling it, a student wanted me to run numbers on it for multiple exit strategies

Each unit was a 1 bed 1 bath (max rent 1000/side after rehab)

With a DSCR loan it would be low cash flow barely $100/month so we took that out.

Two best options he has was to flip it and make 35-40k profit flipping it, getting his first flip under his belt, already has contractor bids who do good work for flippers in the area and a private money lender lined up and it’ll be good experience doing a flip at a young age (he’s only 22)

Or doing a DSCR loan cash out refi and doing an owner finance wrap to a non-bankable buyer and cash flowing $1000/month with about 75k equity in his note that grows over time.

I really do this, and teach people how to invest in real estate.

If you want to learn from me, DM the word MENTOR and I’ll send you a DM with some info 👇👇

Little tour of the new office, everything remodeled from top to bottom.

From a Starbucks coffee shop running comps on a laptop with motuma, and non stop open houses 6-7 years ago with alberto, now a full blown operation.

Nice to just look at the growth and appreciate where we’re headed 🙏

Next Wednesday, I’m going to be hosting a free live seminar master class about how to start structuring your family estate with life insurance, getting your living trust set up and actually adding some of these tools that will protect your family for free! 

I’m not charging for this! 

No, I am not going to try to sell you life insurance, and I am also not trying to make any money from this like most others would.

I simply want the people that help me with these things to help others and inform them especially with a lot of the friends I have who are starting to have children and don’t really know a whole lot about estate planning.

I remember when I was 22 years old in a seminar about estate planning and trusts and everybody else in the room was 65 years or older, and I was the only 20 year old in the room, and I know even though I have this information and I’m implementing this stuff in my life and I’m diversified I  want to impact others in a way that will help bring peace of mind to their families.

if you want to be on this master class and wanna sign up for it SPOTS ARE LIMITED to 100 people, please go to my bio and sign up.

your information will not be shared with anyone 🙏

Let’s start building people up with knowledge and information rather than trying to sell them everything.

After some credits to buyer and closing costs on the double close, we’re at 300k on this one 💪 

Onto the next deal 💰💰💰

Don’t wanna say we’re the biggest wholesale company in CA, but I don’t think anyone is doing the numbers we are with the small team we have. Don’t need 20 people in house to get these kinda multi six figure months.

I see that being taught across the country, and it’s just not the case at least for us.
